│ ### 1. Understanding the Issue                                                             │
│                                                                                            │
│ The `loop-vectorize` pass is aborting due to an assertion failure in                       │
│ `LoopVectorizationPlanner::computeBestVF`. The assertion `(BestFactor.Width ==             │
│ LegacyVF.Width || planContainsAdditionalSimplifications(...)) && "VPlan cost model and     │
